title: Independent candidate Suriya Bibi wins PK-01 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Suriya Bibi has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-01 Chitral Upper by securing 18,914 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, her runner-up was Jamiat Ullma -e- Islam Pakistan (JUI) Shakeel Ahmed who bagged 10,533 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 50.48 percent.
